OL,5, Average petrol prices have fallen below
OL,6, 150p a litre for the first time since  
OL,7, Russia invaded Ukraine, the AA motoring
OL,8, group says.                            
OL,10,FPump prices hit 149.74p per litre on   
OL,11,FMonday, lower than last February and   
OL,12,Fdown from a record 191.53p in July.    
OL,14,FThe AA said falling global oil prices  
OL,15,Fwere behind the drop, calling it "a    
OL,16,Fhuge relief for drivers".              
OL,18,FBut it said diesel still cost more than
OL,19,Flast year at 172.21p a litre compared  
OL,20,Fwith 153.05p.                          
